      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "The free shipping bar is configured separately from your actual shipping rates, which need to be [configured separately](https://help.shopify.com/en/manual/shipping/setting-up-and-managing-your-shipping/free-shipping-rates#free-shipping-over-a-certain-value)."
